OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy to start, this
OL,6,Fclearing to give lengthy sunny spells.
OL,7,FCloud may linger near coasts. Warm or
OL,8,Fvery warm inland, cooler near coasts
OL,9,Fespecially in the breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLow cloud develops over the
OL,12,FNorth Sea and will spread inland to
OL,13,Fcover most of the region by the
OL,14,Fmorning. Light northeasterly wind,
OL,15,Fbreezy along the coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FMorning cloud will burn back
OL,18,Fto the coast during the morning to
OL,19,Fgive sunny spells. Temperatures around
OL,20,For a little above average. Breezy
OL,21,Fnortheasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
